---
// src/components/Features.astro
---

<section class=" w-[90%] rounded-[2.5rem] mx-auto py-24 px-4 relative z-10 bg-slate-50 overflow-hidden">
    
    <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-[0.03] bg-[radial-gradient(#475569_1px,transparent_1px)] [background-size:24px_24px]"></div>

    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto relative z-10">
        
        <div class="text-center mb-16">
            <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-black text-slate-800 mb-4 tracking-tight">
                چرا <span class="text-blue-600">آرم‌فیت پلاس</span> انتخاب پزشکان است؟
            </h2>
            <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm md:text-base max-w-xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
                ترکیبی از دقت پزشکی و هوش مصنوعی پیشرفته، برای اینکه خیال شما از بابت سلامت قلبتان راحت باشد.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 auto-rows-[minmax(180px,auto)]">
            
            <div class="md:col-span-2 bg-white rounded-[2rem] p-8 border border-slate-100 shadow-sm hover:shadow-xl hover:border-blue-100 transition-all duration-500 group relative overflow-hidden">
                <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-32 h-32 bg-blue-50 rounded-bl-[4rem] -mr-4 -mt-4 transition-transform group-hover:scale-110"></div>
                <div class="relative z-10 flex flex-col h-full justify-between">
                    <div class="flex items-start justify-between">
                        <div class="bg-blue-100 p-3 rounded-2xl text-blue-600">
                            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-8 w-8" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M9.75 17L9 20l-1 1h8l-1-1-.75-3M3 13h18M5 17h14a2 2 0 002-2V5a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2z" /></svg>
                        </div>
                        <span class="bg-blue-600 text-white text-[10px] font-bold px-3 py-1 rounded-full">تکنولوژی برتر</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="mt-6">
                        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-800 mb-2">تحلیلگر هوش مصنوعی (AI Doctor)</h3>
                        <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm leading-6">دیگر نگران تفسیر اعداد نباشید. هوش مصنوعی دستگاه، نوار قلب شما را تحلیل کرده و در صورت مشاهده آریتمی یا خطر، بلافاصله هشدار می‌دهد.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-slate-900 rounded-[2rem] p-6 border border-slate-800 shadow-lg relative overflow-hidden group">
                <div class="absolute inset-0 flex items-center justify-center opacity-30">
                    <svg viewBox="0 0 500 150" preserveAspectRatio="none" class="w-full h-24 stroke-emerald-500 fill-none stroke-2">
                        <path d="M0,75 L100,75 L120,25 L140,125 L160,75 L200,75 L220,25 L240,125 L260,75 L500,75" class="animate-ecg-draw" stroke-dasharray="1000" stroke-dashoffset="1000"></path>
                    </svg>
                </div>
                <div class="relative z-10 h-full flex flex-col justify-between">
                    <div class="bg-slate-800 p-3 rounded-2xl w-fit text-emerald-400">
                        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M4.318 6.318a4.5 4.5 0 000 6.364L12 20.364l7.682-7.682a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364-6.364L12 7.636l-1.318-1.318a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364 0z" /></svg>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-1">ECG بیمارستانی</h3>
                        <p class="text-slate-400 text-xs">دقت هم‌تراز با دستگاه‌های کلینیک</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-white rounded-[2rem] p-6 border border-slate-100 shadow-sm hover:shadow-xl hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-500 group relative overflow-hidden">
                
                <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-20 h-20 bg-purple-50 rounded-br-[3rem] -ml-4 -mt-4 transition-transform group-hover:scale-125"></div>

                <div class="relative z-10 flex flex-col h-full justify-between">
                    <div>
                        <div class="bg-purple-100 p-3 rounded-2xl w-fit text-purple-600 mb-4 group-hover:rotate-6 transition-transform shadow-sm">
                            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-7 w-7" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M12 18h.01M8 21h8a2 2 0 002-2V5a2 2 0 00-2-2H8a2 2 0 00-2 2v14a2 2 0 002 2z" /><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M16 3h-3.5" /><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M20 9V7a2 2 0 00-2-2h-2" /><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M4 9V7a2 2 0 012-2h2" /></svg>
                        </div>
                        
                        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-800 mb-2">پایش با اپلیکیشن <span class="text-purple-600">ViHealth</span></h3>
                        <p class="text-slate-500 text-xs leading-6 font-medium">
                            اتصال بلوتوثی آنی به اپلیکیشن قدرتمند ViHealth. نمودارهای نوار قلب را با جزئیات ببینید، تاریخچه فشار خون را ذخیره کنید و گزارش PDF برای پزشک ارسال کنید.
                        </p>
                    </div>

                    <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mt-4 pt-4 border-t border-slate-50 opacity-60 grayscale group-hover:grayscale-0 transition-all">
                        <div class="flex items-center gap-1">
                            <svg class="w-4 h-4" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M17.05 20.28c-.98.95-2.05.8-3.08.35-1.09-.46-2.09-.48-3.24 0-1.44.62-2.2.44-3.06-.35C2.79 15.25 3.51 7.59 9.05 7.31c1.35.07 2.29.74 3.08.74 1.18 0 2.21-.93 3.23-.93 1.2 0 2.38.67 3.21 1.66-3.28 1.68-2.4 5.99 1.03 7.38-.51 1.68-1.19 3.23-2.55 4.12zM12.03 7.25c-.15-2.23 1.66-4.07 3.74-4.25.29 2.58-2.34 4.5-3.74 4.25z"/></svg>
                            <span class="text-[9px] font-bold font-mono">iOS</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="w-px h-3 bg-slate-300"></div>
                        <div class="flex items-center gap-1">
                            <svg class="w-4 h-4" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M17.523 15.3414C17.523 16.7249 16.402 17.8459 15.0186 17.8459C13.6351 17.8459 12.5142 16.7249 12.5142 15.3414C12.5142 13.958 13.6351 12.837 15.0186 12.837C16.402 12.837 17.523 13.958 17.523 15.3414ZM7.5062 15.3414C7.5062 16.7249 6.38525 17.8459 5.00181 17.8459C3.61837 17.8459 2.49742 16.7249 2.49742 15.3414C2.49742 13.958 3.61837 12.837 5.00181 12.837C6.38525 12.837 7.5062 13.958 7.5062 15.3414ZM10.0092 5.7291L9.2376 3.4143C9.15745 3.15385 8.87705 3.0136 8.6166 3.09375C8.35615 3.1739 8.2159 3.4543 8.29605 3.71475L9.01725 5.90945C6.1048 7.2317 4.04017 9.99645 3.57937 13.3379H16.4408C15.98 9.99645 13.9154 7.2317 11.0029 5.90945L11.7241 3.71475C11.8043 3.4543 11.664 3.1739 11.4036 3.09375C11.1431 3.0136 10.8627 3.15385 10.7826 3.4143L10.0092 5.7291Z"/></svg>
                            <span class="text-[9px] font-bold font-mono">Android</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="md:col-span-2 bg-gradient-to-br from-white to-slate-50 rounded-[2rem] p-8 border border-slate-100 shadow-sm hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-500 flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center gap-8">
                <div class="flex-1">
                    <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
                        <div class="bg-orange-100 p-2 rounded-xl text-orange-600">
                            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z" /></svg>
                        </div>
                        <span class="text-orange-600 font-bold text-xs bg-orange-50 px-2 py-1 rounded-lg">شارژدهی طولانی</span>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-800 mb-2">بدون نیاز به تعویض باتری</h3>
                    <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm leading-6">با باتری لیتیومی قابل شارژ، با یک بار شارژ تا ۵۰۰ بار فشار خون بگیرید. طراحی ارگونومیک کاف (بازوبند) باعث می‌شود هیچ فشاری روی دست حس نکنید.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="w-full md:w-48 h-24 bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-inner border border-slate-100 flex items-center justify-center relative overflow-hidden">
                    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-green-50"></div>
                    <div class="flex items-center gap-2 z-10">
                        <span class="text-3xl font-black text-green-600">30</span>
                        <span class="text-xs font-bold text-slate-400 flex flex-col leading-3">
                            <span>روز</span>
                            <span>استندبای</span>
                        </span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<style>
    @keyframes draw {
        0% { stroke-dashoffset: 1000; }
        100% { stroke-dashoffset: 0; }
    }
    .animate-ecg-draw {
        animation: draw 4s linear infinite;
    }
</style>